OL,3,CThe women haunted by forced adoptions
OL,4,Clooking for answers
OL,6,FA special report from ITV News Social
OL,7,FAffairs Correspondent Sarah Corker on
OL,8,Fthe lasting trauma for the tens of
OL,9,Fthousands of women forced to give up
OL,10,Ftheir babies for adoption
OL,12,FWarning: Readers may find some of the
OL,13,Fissues discussed in this article to be
OL,14,Fdistressing
OL,16,FIn the decades after the war, nearly
OL,17,F200,000 unmarried women were forced
OL,18,Fand shamed into giving up their babies
OL,19,Ffor adoption in England and Wales.
