OL,3,CThe women haunted by forced adoptions
OL,4,Clooking for answers
OL,6,FThis is the harrowing story of mothers
OL,7,Fstill traumatised by the cruelty they
OL,8,Ffaced for getting pregnant out of
OL,9,Fwedlock, and their decades-long search
OL,10,Ffor justice.
OL,12,FBetween 1949 and the mid 1970s,
OL,13,Fthousands of women were sent away to
OL,14,Fmother and baby homes run by churches
OL,15,Fand the state - places of secrecy,
OL,16,Fcruelty and even abuse - where babies
OL,17,Fwere put up for adoption or died
OL,18,Fthrough poor care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
