OL,6,FITV News has investigated one home in
OL,7,Fsouth Cumbria. Burial records obtained
OL,8,Fthrough a Freedom of Information
OL,9,Frequest revealed that 45 babies are
OL,10,Fburied in unmarked graves close to the
OL,11,Finstitution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
