OL,3,CThe women haunted by forced adoptions
OL,4,Clooking for answers
OL,6,FDr Michael Lambert, an academic
OL,7,Fspecialising in the welfare state at
OL,8,FLancaster University, has spent years
OL,9,Finvestigating the disturbing
OL,10,Fconditions inside some of these homes
OL,11,Ffor unmarried mothers; St Monica's, in
OL,12,FKendal, which was operated by the
OL,13,FChurch of England's Diocese of
OL,14,FCarlisle from 1918 until its closure
OL,15,Fin 1970, was the "worst he's come
OL,16,Facross".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
