OL,3,CThe women haunted by forced adoptions
OL,4,Clooking for answers
OL,6,FDr Lambert showed me page after page
OL,7,Fof official council and government
OL,8,Fdocuments that warned of sub-standard
OL,9,Fmedical treatment, a lack of trained
OL,10,Fmidwives and harsh, even punitive
OL,11,Fconditions.
OL,13,F"Women there were effectively being
OL,14,Fdenied access to modern medicine and I
OL,15,Fthink that is why so many (babies) are
OL,16,Fdying at such a young age," he told
OL,17,FITV News.
OL,19,F"Even by the standards of that time,
OL,20,Fmortality rates were high at the
OL,21,Fhome," he said.
