OL,3,CThe women haunted by forced adoptions
OL,4,Clooking for answers
OL,6,FOur investigation took us to Parkside
OL,7,FCemetery in Kendal. Official records
OL,8,Fshow that 45 babies are buried in an
OL,9,Funmarked plot - all lived and died at
OL,10,Fthe home.
OL,12,FThe youngest survived for just 45
OL,13,Fminutes, the oldest, 11 weeks. There
OL,14,Fis now a local campaign for headstones
OL,15,Fto be erected to remember all 45
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
