OL,6,F'I think out there, there is a lot of
OL,7,Fshame and people feeling very stuck
OL,8,Fabout the fact that happened to them
OL,9,Fduring that period... they haven't had
OL,10,Fa chance to make that right for
OL,11,Fthemselves,' PAC-UK Family Action's
OL,12,FMike Hancock told ITV News
OL,14,FAfter decades of silence and secrecy,
OL,15,Fadoption support charities say more
OL,16,Fwomen, many now in their 80s and 90s,
OL,17,Fare coming forward to access their
OL,18,Ffiles, trace their children and seek
OL,19,Fsupport. At one time there were 150
OL,20,Fhomes for unmarried mothers in England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
