OL,6,F"For many of those birth mothers, they
OL,7,Fwere told to go home and not talk to
OL,8,Fanybody about what had happened to
OL,9,Fthem," said Mike Hancock from PAC-UK
OL,10,FFamily Action, the country's largest
OL,11,Findependent adoption support agency.
OL,13,F"They held on to these secrets very
OL,14,Ftightly and I think that is incredibly
OL,15,Fdamaging. There is still a lot of
OL,16,Fshame, trauma and many women have
OL,17,Fnever spoken about this," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
