OL,3,CThe women haunted by forced adoptions
OL,4,Clooking for answers
OL,6,F"I was told 'you'd be selfish to keep
OL,7,Fyour baby. If you love your baby you
OL,8,Fwill give them up', that's what they
OL,9,Ftold all of us," she told ITV News.
OL,11,F"'They' being the family GP, the
OL,12,Fmidwives, and the moral welfare
OL,13,Fofficers as they were known at the
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,F"We were shown into a room and a lady
OL,17,Fasked if she could hold my son, then
OL,18,Fshe said 'kiss him goodbye' and I knew
OL,19,Fthat was the last time I would ever
OL,20,Fsee him. It was a terribly cruel way
OL,21,Fto treat mothers and children."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
