OL,6,FMs Killington, now 73, was even forced
OL,7,Fto sign a legal document promising to
OL,8,Fnever look for her son.
OL,10,F27 years later she received a letter
OL,11,Ffrom the other side of the world that
OL,12,Ftook her breath away. Her son, Ian
OL,13,FPritchard, had been searching for his
OL,14,Fmother.
OL,16,FIan Pritchard, whose mother Jill was
OL,17,Fforced to give him up for adoption,
OL,18,Ftold ITV News that 'a lot of different
OL,19,Fareas' of his life were impacted by
OL,20,Fthe scandal
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
