OL,6,FHis adoptive family had moved to New
OL,7,FZealand when he was just six, and as
OL,8,Fan adult he'd battled addiction and
OL,9,Fmental health challenges.
OL,11,F"It (my adoption) caused me a lot of
OL,12,Fdespair, pain and confusion," Mr
OL,13,FPritchard said.
OL,15,F"We didn't get a choice, Jill didn't
OL,16,Fget a choice because that choice was
OL,17,Ftaken from her when I was removed from
OL,18,Fher and I certainly didn't get a
OL,19,Fchoice in any of this."
