OL,6,FIn the years since their reunion, Jill
OL,7,Fand Ian have forged a strong bond.
OL,9,FIn 2022, an inquiry by the Joint
OL,10,FCommittee on Human Rights concluded
OL,11,Fthat the government bore ultimate
OL,12,Fresponsibility for the "pain and
OL,13,Fsuffering" caused by public
OL,14,Finstitutions and state employees'
OL,15,Finvolved in "cruel" forced adoptions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
