OL,6,FThe UK government has previously said
OL,7,Fit was sorry "on behalf of society"
OL,8,Ffor what happened, but unlike the
OL,9,FWelsh, Scottish and Irish governments
OL,10,Fhas not formally apologised for its
OL,11,Frole in forced adoptions.
OL,13,FA Department for Education
OL,14,Fspokesperson said: "We have the
OL,15,Fdeepest sympathy with all of those who
OL,16,Fare affected by historic forced
OL,17,Fadoption. The practice was abhorrent
OL,18,Fand should never have taken place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
