OL,6,F"We will look to learn from the
OL,7,Fapproach of the devolved nations, and
OL,8,Fwill explore what more can be done to
OL,9,Fsupport those impacted."
OL,11,FIn relation to allegations of neglect
OL,12,Fand abuse at St Monica's Mother and
OL,13,FBaby Home in Cumbria, a spokesperson
OL,14,Ffor The Diocese of Carlisle described
OL,15,Fthe accounts as "shocking" and said
OL,16,F"we are deeply sorry that people
OL,17,Fsuffered in this way".
