OL,6,F"We were made aware of the burial of
OL,7,Fbabies who had died at St Monica's in
OL,8,Fan area of Parkside Cemetery in
OL,9,FKendal," a statement read.
OL,11,F"We immediately alerted Cumbria
OL,12,FConstabulary and have continued to
OL,13,Fensure they have had access to all
OL,14,Favailable records."
OL,16,FAnyone affected by the issues raised
OL,17,Fin this report can contact the
OL,18,FDiocesan Safeguarding Adviser at
OL,19,Fsafeguarding.adviser@carlislediocese.org
OL,20,For Safe Spaces at
