OL,6,FCumbria Constabulary told ITV News
OL,7,Fthat "to date, no crimes have been
OL,8,Fidentified", in relation to the former
OL,9,FSt Monica's home and Parkside Road
OL,10,FCemetery in Kendal.
OL,12,FWhile Westmorland and Furness Council
OL,13,Fand Cumberland Council explained that
OL,14,Fburials in "unpurchased or public
OL,15,Fgraves were fairly common" as
OL,16,F"families often didn't have sufficient
OL,17,Fresources to pay for a funeral".
